RIYADH: Saudi Arabia welcomes and congratulates Sudan on the launch of the final phase of the political process in the country, the foreign ministry said on Sunday. The Kingdom also congratulates Sudan on the measures taken to prioritize this process, and to implement measures to create a climate of trust between all parties, the ministry added. The Kingdom also commended the international efforts of the UN Mission in Sudan, the African Union, and the Intergovernmental Authority on Development, affirming its permanent support for the return of political stability to Sudan. The ministry said the Kingdom continues efforts to achieve stability, development, and prosperity in Sudan in conjunction with the Friends of Sudan group and other international partners.